{How to continue here?} 5. a4 $5 {This has been played only once out of 700+
games. We want to gain further space with a5 in the future. We are also
waiting for Black to commit to a plan to develop his kingside.} c6 (5... Be7 {
This is usually an indication to go Ng3-f5.} 6. Ng3 O-O 7. Be2 c6 8. O-O $14 {
Nf5 is coming up next.}) 6. a5 {This pawn will be a thorn in Black's position
for a long time. We always have the idea of going a6.} Be7 7. Ng3 O-O 8. Be2 g6
