{How to continue here?} 11. g4 $1 {Change of plans. After Black has partially
closed the center with e5 we are going to start an initiative on the kingside.
Our king is pretty safe on e1 and can castle any side, any time.} f5 12. Qb3 e4
13. Ng5 f4 (13... h6 14. O-O-O hxg5 15. c5 $18) 14. Bc5 Bxc3+ 15. bxc3 f3 16.
Bf1 Nexd5 17. h4 $1 $18 {All of Black's pieces are hanging and he is in huge
trouble.} *

