pawn structure.} (12. c4 Nbd7 13. a3 Re8 14. Re1 Ne4 15. Rc1 Bg6 16. Nc3 Nxc3
17. Rxc3 $16 {1-0 (44) Vachier Lagrave,M (2760) -Tiviakov,S (2570) Chartres
